title: Strike delays hit Australian airports : September 21, 2015,
text:
Strike delays hit Australian airports... Strike delays hit Australian airports : September 21, 2015, Next Story Prev Story 1 hr ago Read more: Daily Times 
SYDNEY Travellers using Australia's international airports faced delays on Monday and was warned of more to come as immigration and border force workers went on strike over pay and conditions. Morning peak-hour travel was held up with long queues forming in Sydney, which along with airports in Perth, Melbourne, Brisbane, Adelaide, Darwin, Coolangatta and Cairns experienced two-hour stoppages when staff walked out.   Daily Times.
